{"lemma":"مَوْصُولٌ","slug":"مَوْصُولٌ","root":"#.ص.ل","root_slug":"_-ص-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ص-ل","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n44621"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D8%B5%D9%8F%D9%88%D9%84%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"connected, linked, attached"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"relative pronoun"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the passive participle of وَصَلَ (waṣala, “to connect”)."},"ipa":["/maw.sˤuːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n44621","headword_ar":"مَوْصُولٌ","root":"wSl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", in grammar, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A conjunct"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. This is of two kinds;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawoSuwlN HarofiY~N","text_ar":"مَوْصُولٌ حَرْفِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawoSuwlN A_isomiY~N","text_ar":"مَوْصُولٌ اـِسْمِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". The former term [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conjunct particle"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is applied to the infinitive particles"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano","text_ar":"اَنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^an~a","text_ar":"اَنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaY","text_ar":"كَى"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lawo","text_ar":"لَوْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA","text_ar":"مَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". The latter term [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conjunct noun"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (I have thus rendered it voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^alo","text_ar":"اَلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ino","text_ar":"اـِنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a","text_ar":"اـِنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":") is applied to the conjunctive nouns"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^al~a*iY","text_ar":"اَلَّذِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", and its fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aal~atiY","text_ar":"اَلَّتِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano","text_ar":"مَنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA","text_ar":"مَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw","text_ar":"ذُو"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the dial. of Teiyi, and to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aalo","text_ar":"اَلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which last some incorrectly hold to be a conjunct particle, and others assert to be a determinative particle and not a conjunct, and to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aA","text_ar":"ذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"after the interrogative"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA","text_ar":"مَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano","text_ar":"مَنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (I' Ak, sect."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmawoSuwlu","text_ar":"المَوْصُولُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B5%D9%88%D9%84/","headword_ar":"موصول","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23783#66a758","body_html":"<span>الموصول: ما لا يكون جزءًا تامًا إلا بصلة وعائد.</span>"}]}}